Directed by Vishvak Khanderao

Written by Vishvak Khanderao

Star Mahaboob Basha (Meesam Saidulu (archive footage)).Tanikella Bharani . Cricknowle (Sunny). Satyadev Kancharana. Nithya Menen (Gowri). Bhanu Prakash (Chotu).Rahul Ramakrishna . Aripirala Satyaprasad (Ramesh). Meesam Suresh (Sambha villager). Tulasi. Vishnu Vijay

Language Telugu

Producers Nithya Menen. Pravallika Pinnamaraju. Prithvi Pinnamaraju. Naresh Reddy Polasani

Production Byte Features. Nithya Menen Company
